{"tid":1261150,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"對於新香港國花問題，可揀宮粉羊蹄甲","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T08:24:56.000Z","uid":122054,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8affb230c0f5704de9ca8ca0ef7d1dfe727f7de5","tid":1261150,"uid":122054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"以花為旗係冇錯既<br />\n<br />\n問題係洋紫荊係mix所以絕後<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AE%AE%E7%B2%89%E7%BE%8A%E8%B9%84%E7%94%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25BE%258A%25E8%25B9%2584%25E7%2594%25B2&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=1c447c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AE%AE%E7%B2%89%E7%BE%8A%E8%B9%84%E7%94%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n羊蹄甲（學名：Bauhinia variegata）是一種豆科蘇木亞科羊蹄甲屬的有花植物，為一種落葉小喬木，俗稱蘭花木、印度櫻花、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">南洋櫻花</span></span></strong>、馬蹄豆、白花羊紫荊；羊蹄甲，中國大陸稱為洋紫荊，港澳稱為宮粉羊蹄甲。原產於中國南部、印度及馬來半島。羊蹄甲於每年3月至5月落葉後開花，花有5枚粉紅色的花瓣，其中1枚有深紅色條紋。而不少人將此花與同屬屬的艷紫荊混淆，主要分別在於後者開花期不同，艷紫荊的開花期為秋天（11月前後）並且在開花時葉茂盛。<br />\n<br />\n呢種花絕對算係東南亞當中其中算係靚既花<br />\n大家唔好ban洋紫荊就ban埋佢親戚羊蹄甲<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"f0d1a250c6e9781132d1ae3348b92f9194d3ef9f","tid":1261150,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"白蘭花"},{"pid":"63c1cc3e7dce0d1a4c08fa5ceab08c5a9f0af98d","tid":1261150,"uid":35231,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"做咩一定要搵花代表HK<br />\n我寧願要一把遮/一粒魚蛋"},{"pid":"3eda38acd65228efb6aff2c409130907279f94a2","tid":1261150,"uid":255557,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"連個幾大訴求都未搞掂你ff新國花做乜"},{"pid":"d046efb267f71d242d12d193f17b0c638a9b4d15","tid":1261150,"uid":159307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"支持用雨傘"},{"pid":"a294fe14031cd